set default deny

interface lan = "eth1"
interface wan = "eth0"

queue std on wan bandwidth 10M
queue voip on wan bandwidth 1M parent std

nat on wan from 10.0.0.0/24 to any -> wan
rdr on wan proto tcp from any to any port 80 -> 10.0.0.5 port 8080

pass in on lan from 10.0.0.0/24 to any queue std
pass out on wan proto tcp from any to any port 443 route-to 1.1.1.1 (wan) keep state
